====================================
 XuBooth README
====================================


Software requirements
--------------------------------------------
 - git-core			# downloading/updating XuBooth
 - gphoto2			# camera tethering software
 - eog				# image viewer
 - feh				# slideshow tool
 - exiftool			# customization of photos' EXIF data
 - graphicsmagick		# applying overlays and other graphics onto the photos
 - hostapd			# wifi access point for Over-The-Air
 - dnsmasq			# DNS/DHCP server for Over-The-Air
 - lighttpd			# web server for Over-The-Air
 - php-cgi			# php5 module for Over-The-Air
 - dialog			# CLI-based menu creation tool (used for e.g. choosing one of several XuBooth configurations)


Install requirements on Debian/Ubuntu
--------------------------------------------
sudo apt-get install git-core gphoto2 eog feh exiftool graphicsmagick hostapd dnsmasq lighttpd php-cgi dialog


Getting a working copy
--------------------------------------------
 - git clone https://github.com/theboothbrothers/XuBooth.git


Cleaning the working copy
--------------------------------------------
 1) remove any new files you added (config files and images are ignored)
	git clean -df

 2) undo any changes you might have done to the source code
	git checkout origin/master -- .


Updating the working copy
--------------------------------------------
 - git pull origin master
